Author: BitBot software developers from UCI.
This is version 1.0 of our chess software "Kingdoms!".
To install, please type make. 
To start the Game, please type ./bin/chess.
To test, please type make test.
Our program supports choosing color, choosing mode, playing vs your friend, playing vs the computer.
The software let you undo your move, and it displays very clear messages in case of errors.
For more instructions, please refer to the user manual and software specefication files.
This version is released on Sunday February 4. 

